longBusinessSummary: Nabors Energy Transition Corp. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. It intends to acquire companies in the alternative energy, energy storage, emissions reduction, carbon capture, and utilization and sequestration sectors. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Houston, Texas.
